00:00:13.112 --> 00:00:14.437
Habari

00:00:14.461 --> 00:00:16.807
Ngoja niiulize hadhira swali:

00:00:16.831 --> 00:00:19.026
Ulishawahi kudanganya ukiwa mtoto?

00:00:19.050 --> 00:00:21.717
Kama uliwahi, unaweza
kunyanyua mkono tafadhali?

00:00:23.145 --> 00:00:26.599
Wow! hili ni kundi la watu wakweli
kuliko wote niliowahi kukutana nao.

00:00:26.623 --> 00:00:28.580
(Kicheko)

00:00:28.604 --> 00:00:30.313
Hadi sasa kwa miaka 20 iliyopita,

00:00:30.337 --> 00:00:33.752
Nimekuwa nikisoma
jinsi watoto wanavyojifunza kudanganya.

00:00:33.776 --> 00:00:36.080
Na leo, nitawashirikisha

00:00:36.104 --> 00:00:38.266
baadhi ya ugunduzi tulioupata.

00:00:38.624 --> 00:00:43.549
Ila kwa kuanza, nitawaambia
hadithi kutoka kwa Bwana Richard Messina,

00:00:43.573 --> 00:00:46.702
ambaye ni rafiki yangu na mkuu wa
shule ya msingi.

00:00:47.266 --> 00:00:48.827
Alipokea simu siku moja.

00:00:51.279 --> 00:00:52.430
Aliyepiga akasema,

00:00:52.454 --> 00:00:56.336
"Bwana Messina, mtoto wangu Johnny
hatakuja shuleni leo

00:00:56.360 --> 00:00:57.823
kwasababu anaumwa."

00:00:58.498 --> 00:01:00.234
Bwana Messina akauliza,

00:01:00.258 --> 00:01:02.272
"Naongea na nani, tafadhali?"

00:01:02.788 --> 00:01:04.278
Na aliyepiga akasema,

00:01:04.302 --> 00:01:05.967
"Mimi ni baba yangu."

00:01:05.991 --> 00:01:08.778
(Kicheko)

00:01:10.227 --> 00:01:11.909
Sasa hadithi hii --

00:01:11.933 --> 00:01:13.465
(Vicheko)

00:01:13.489 --> 00:01:17.799
inajumlisha vizuri sana
imani tatu zilizo zoeleka tulizonazo

00:01:17.823 --> 00:01:19.682
kuhusu watoto na kudanganya.

00:01:20.140 --> 00:01:24.771
Moja, watoto huja tu kusema uongo

00:01:24.795 --> 00:01:27.063
baada ya kuingia shule ya msingi.

00:01:27.552 --> 00:01:29.863
Mbili, watoto hawadanganyi vizuri.

00:01:29.887 --> 00:01:32.744
Watu wazima twaweza kugundua uwongo wao.

00:01:32.768 --> 00:01:36.806
Na tatu, kama watoto watadanganya
katika umri mdogo sana,

00:01:36.830 --> 00:01:39.679
lazima watakuwa na makosa
kitabia,

00:01:39.703 --> 00:01:43.752
na watakuja kuwa
wagonjwa wa kudanganya maishani.

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:46.914
Hivyo inaonekana kwamba

00:01:46.938 --> 00:01:49.236
imani zote tatu hazikuwa sahihi.

00:01:50.617 --> 00:01:53.327
Tumekuwa tukifanya mchezo wa kukisia

00:01:53.351 --> 00:01:55.433
na watoto dunia nzima.

00:01:55.457 --> 00:01:56.943
Huu ni mfano

00:01:56.967 --> 00:02:01.332
Hivyo katika mchezo huu, tunauliza watoto
kukisia namba kwenye kadi.

00:02:01.958 --> 00:02:04.836
Na tunawaambia wakishinda mchezo,

00:02:04.860 --> 00:02:07.017
watapata zawadi kubwa.

00:02:07.525 --> 00:02:09.002
Lakini katikati ya mchezo,

00:02:09.026 --> 00:02:11.786
tunatoa udhuru na kutoka kwenye chumba.

00:02:13.763 --> 00:02:15.697
Na kabla ya kutoka kwenye chumba,

00:02:15.721 --> 00:02:18.657
tunawaambia wasichungulie kwenye kadi.

00:02:19.518 --> 00:02:20.934
Bila shaka,

00:02:20.958 --> 00:02:23.119
tuna kamera zilizofichwa katika chumba

00:02:23.143 --> 00:02:24.938
kuangalia kila hatua yao.

00:02:26.216 --> 00:02:29.633
Kwasababu haja ya kushinda
mchezo ni kubwa sana,

00:02:29.657 --> 00:02:33.143
zaidi ya asilimia 90 ya watoto 
watachungulia

00:02:33.167 --> 00:02:34.604
mara tutakapotoka chumbani.

00:02:34.628 --> 00:02:36.628
(Kicheko)

00:02:37.044 --> 00:02:39.030
Swali la msingi ni:

00:02:39.054 --> 00:02:41.802
Tutakaporudi na kuuliza watoto

00:02:41.826 --> 00:02:44.135
Kama wamechungulia au la,

00:02:44.159 --> 00:02:47.211
watoto waliochungulia watakiri

00:02:47.235 --> 00:02:49.813
au watadanganya kuhusu makosa yao?

00:02:51.525 --> 00:02:56.298
Tuligundua kwamba bila kujali
jinsia, nchi, au dini,

00:02:56.934 --> 00:02:58.513
katika umri wa miaka miwili,

00:02:59.188 --> 00:03:01.115
asilimia 30 hudanganya,

00:03:01.139 --> 00:03:04.948
asilimia 70 husema ukweli
kuhusu makosa yao.

00:03:04.972 --> 00:03:07.110
Katika umri wa miaka mitatu,

00:03:07.134 --> 00:03:10.608
asilimia 50 hudanganya na asilimia 50
husema kweli.

00:03:11.302 --> 00:03:13.201
Katika umri wa miaka minne,

00:03:13.225 --> 00:03:15.172
zaidi ya asilimia 80 hudanganya.

00:03:16.334 --> 00:03:18.785
Na baada ya miaka minne,

00:03:18.809 --> 00:03:20.198
watoto wengi hudanganya.

00:03:21.180 --> 00:03:22.543
Hivyo unaweza kuona,

00:03:22.567 --> 00:03:26.030
kudanganya ni sehemu halisi
ya kuendelea.

00:03:26.054 --> 00:03:28.844
Na baadhi ya watoto huanza kusema uwongo

00:03:28.868 --> 00:03:31.307
wakiwa na umri mdogo wa miaka miwili.

00:03:32.438 --> 00:03:35.995
Hivyo sasa, tuangalie kwa ukaribu
watoto wadogo.

00:03:37.336 --> 00:03:41.149
Kwanini baadhi na sio wote
watoto wadogo hudanganya?

00:03:42.184 --> 00:03:45.513
Katika mapishi unahitaji viungo vizuri

00:03:45.537 --> 00:03:47.150
kupika chakula kizuri.

00:03:47.793 --> 00:03:52.356
Na uongo mzuri unahitaji 
viungo viwili vikuu.

00:03:53.109 --> 00:03:57.219
Kiungo kikuu cha kwanza
ni nadharia ya akili,

00:03:57.243 --> 00:03:59.078
au uwezo wa kusoma- akili.

00:03:59.768 --> 00:04:01.846
Kusoma akili ni uwezo wa kujua

00:04:01.870 --> 00:04:06.478
kwamba watu tofauti wana
ufahamu tofauti kuhusu hali fulani

00:04:06.502 --> 00:04:10.303
na uwezo wa kutofautisha
kati ya ninachojua

00:04:10.327 --> 00:04:11.550
na kile unachojua

00:04:11.914 --> 00:04:14.161
Kusoma akili ni muhimu kwa kudanganya

00:04:14.185 --> 00:04:18.032
kwasababu ya msingi wa kudanganya ni najua

00:04:18.056 --> 00:04:19.207
hujui

00:04:19.231 --> 00:04:20.382
ninachojua.

00:04:20.406 --> 00:04:21.777
Hivyo, naweza kukudanganya.

00:04:23.070 --> 00:04:27.680
Kiungo cha pili muhimu

00:04:27.704 --> 00:04:32.327
Ni uwezo wa kudhibiti maneno yako,
kuonyesha hisia usoni

00:04:32.351 --> 00:04:33.891
na lugha ya mwili,

00:04:33.915 --> 00:04:35.993
ili kwamba unaweza kusema uongo thabiti.

00:04:36.938 --> 00:04:40.664
Na tulikuta kwamba wale watoto wadogo

00:04:40.688 --> 00:04:45.544
walio na uwezo mkubwa wa kusoma akili
na uwezo wa kujidhibiti

00:04:45.568 --> 00:04:47.606
husema uwongo mapema

00:04:47.630 --> 00:04:50.446
na ni waongo wa kisasa.

00:04:51.887 --> 00:04:57.506
Kama inavyokuwa, uwezo huu wa aina mbili
ni muhimu pia kwetu sote

00:04:57.530 --> 00:05:00.052
kuweza kufanya kazi katika jamii yetu.

00:05:00.848 --> 00:05:05.183
Ki ukweli, kushindwa kusoma akili
na uwezo wa kujidhibiti

00:05:05.207 --> 00:05:08.766
vinahusianishwa na matatizo makubwa
ya ukuaji,

00:05:08.790 --> 00:05:11.549
kama ADHD na usonji.

00:05:13.893 --> 00:05:19.070
Hivyo ukigundua mtoto wako wa miaka miwili
anakudanganya kwa mara ya kwanza,

00:05:19.094 --> 00:05:21.078
badala ya kushtushwa,

00:05:21.102 --> 00:05:22.594
unatakiwa usherehekee--

00:05:22.618 --> 00:05:24.140
(Kicheko)

00:05:24.164 --> 00:05:29.894
kwasababu inaashiria kwamba mtoto wako
amefikia hatua mpya

00:05:29.918 --> 00:05:31.553
ya ukuaji wa kawaida.

00:05:33.085 --> 00:05:36.221
Sasa, watoto hawadanganyi vizuri?

00:05:36.878 --> 00:05:39.872
Unafikiri unaweza kugundua
udanganyifu wao kirahisi?

00:05:40.745 --> 00:05:42.423
Ungependa kujaribu?

00:05:42.921 --> 00:05:44.401
Ndio? Sawa.

00:05:44.425 --> 00:05:46.564
Sasa nitakuonyesha video mbili

00:05:47.024 --> 00:05:48.175
Kwenye video,

00:05:48.199 --> 00:05:51.256
watoto watajibu maswali ya
utafiti,

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:52.762
"Ulichungulia?"

00:05:52.786 --> 00:05:54.340
Sasa jaribu kuniambia

00:05:54.364 --> 00:05:55.762
mtoto yupi anadanganya

00:05:55.786 --> 00:05:57.896
na mtoto yupi anasema ukweli.

00:05:58.272 --> 00:05:59.991
Huyu ni mtoto namba moja.

00:06:00.991 --> 00:06:02.228
Uko tayari?

00:06:03.006 --> 00:06:04.926
(Video) Mtu: Ulichungulia? Mtoto: Hapana

00:06:05.619 --> 00:06:07.855
Kang Lee: Na huyu ni mtoto namba mbili.

00:06:09.501 --> 00:06:11.693
(Video) Mtu: Ulichungulia? Mtoto: Hapana.

00:06:13.296 --> 00:06:16.883
KL: OK, kama unafikiri
mtoto namba moja anadanganya,

00:06:16.907 --> 00:06:18.594
