00:06:20.401 --> 00:06:23.953
Na kama unafikiri mtoto namba mbili
anadanganya, tafadhali inua mkono wako.

00:06:25.593 --> 00:06:28.067
OK, kusema ukweli,

00:06:28.091 --> 00:06:31.028
mtoto namba moja anasema ukweli,

00:06:31.052 --> 00:06:33.081
mtoto namba mbili anadanganya.

00:06:34.124 --> 00:06:37.354
Inaonekana wengi wenu sio wagunduzi
wazuri wa uwongo wa watoto.

00:06:37.378 --> 00:06:39.856
(Kicheko)

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:43.264
Sasa, tumeshiriki kwenye michezo sawasawa

00:06:43.288 --> 00:06:47.913
na watu wazima wengi sana
kutoka sehemu zote za maisha.

00:06:48.714 --> 00:06:50.872
Na tunawaonyesha video nyingi.

00:06:51.347 --> 00:06:53.896
Katika nusu ya video, watoto walidanganya.

00:06:53.920 --> 00:06:57.187
Katika nusu ya video nyingine,
watoto walisema ukweli.

00:06:58.529 --> 00:07:01.386
Ngoja tuone 
watu wazima hawa walifanyaje.

00:07:02.319 --> 00:07:06.174
Kwasababu kuna waongo wengi
kama wasema kweli,

00:07:06.198 --> 00:07:08.597
ukikisia kwa kubahatisha,

00:07:08.621 --> 00:07:12.691
kunauwezekano wa asilimia 50
ukapatia.

00:07:12.715 --> 00:07:16.309
Hivyo ikiwa usahihi wako ni takriban 
asilimia 50,

00:07:16.333 --> 00:07:19.774
inamaanisha wewe ni mgunduzi mbaya
wa uwongo wa watoto.

00:07:20.290 --> 00:07:24.819
Sasa tuanze na wanafunzi wa shahada
ya kwanza na wanafunzi wa sheria,

00:07:24.843 --> 00:07:28.515
ambao kwa ujumla
hawana uzoefu na watoto.

00:07:30.038 --> 00:07:32.000
Hapana hawawezi kugundua uwongo wa watoto

00:07:32.024 --> 00:07:34.238
Utendaji wao ni wa kubahatisha

00:07:34.262 --> 00:07:39.491
Sasa vipi kuhusu wafanyakazi za jamii
na walinda haki za watoto,

00:07:39.515 --> 00:07:42.189
wanaofanyakazi na watoto kila siku?

00:07:42.213 --> 00:07:44.300
Wanaweza kugundua uwongo wa watoto?

00:07:45.624 --> 00:07:46.775
Hapana, hawawezi,

00:07:46.799 --> 00:07:47.844
(Kicheko)

00:07:47.868 --> 00:07:49.340
Vipi kuhusu majaji,

00:07:49.364 --> 00:07:51.164
maafisa forodha

00:07:51.188 --> 00:07:53.046
na maafisa polisi,

00:07:53.070 --> 00:07:55.713
wanaokutana na wadanganyifu kila siku?

00:07:55.737 --> 00:07:57.654
Wanaweza kugundua uwongo wa watoto?

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:00.014
Hapana hawawezi.

00:08:00.430 --> 00:08:01.616
Vipi kuhusu wazazi?

00:08:01.640 --> 00:08:04.654
Wazazi wanaweza kugundua uwongo wa watoto
wengine?

00:08:05.898 --> 00:08:07.136
Hapana, hawawezi.

00:08:07.821 --> 00:08:11.406
Inawezekana wazazi
kugundua uwongo wa watoto wao wenyewe?

00:08:13.208 --> 00:08:14.409
Hapana, hawawezi.

00:08:14.433 --> 00:08:17.909
(Kicheko) (Makofi)

00:08:17.933 --> 00:08:19.480
Hivyo sasa unaweza kuuliza

00:08:20.504 --> 00:08:24.136
kwanini uwongo wa watoto
ni vigumu kuugundua.

00:08:24.958 --> 00:08:27.970
Ngoja niwaonyeshe hili
na mtoto wangu mwenyewe, Nathan

00:08:27.994 --> 00:08:30.163
Hii ni hisia za uso wake

00:08:30.187 --> 00:08:31.571
anapodanganya.

00:08:31.595 --> 00:08:33.801
(Kicheko)

00:08:33.825 --> 00:08:35.427
Hivyo wakati watoto wanadanganya,

00:08:35.451 --> 00:08:38.607
hisia za nyuso zao
ni za kawaida.

00:08:39.123 --> 00:08:42.583
Ingawa nyuma ya hii hisia ya kawaida,

00:08:42.607 --> 00:08:45.933
mtoto kiukweli hupitia
hisia nyingi,

00:08:45.957 --> 00:08:49.812
kama hofu, hatia, fedheha

00:08:49.836 --> 00:08:52.932
na pengine raha ya kudanganya kidogo.

00:08:52.956 --> 00:08:55.658
(Kicheko)

00:08:55.682 --> 00:09:00.522
Bahati mbaya, hisia za aina hiyo
ni aidha za muda mfupi au zimejificha

00:09:00.546 --> 00:09:03.645
Kwahiyo, ni ambazo hazionekani kwetu.

00:09:03.669 --> 00:09:05.028
Kwa miaka mitano iliyopita,

00:09:05.052 --> 00:09:08.948
tumekuwa tukijaribu kutafuta njia
ya kuonyesha hisia hizi zilizojificha.

00:09:08.972 --> 00:09:10.486
Kisha tukapata ugunduzi.

00:09:11.273 --> 00:09:14.458
Tunajua kwamba chini ya ngozi 
za nyuso zetu,

00:09:14.482 --> 00:09:17.876
kuna mtandao mkubwa wa mishipa ya damu.

00:09:17.900 --> 00:09:20.317
Tunapopitia hisia tofauti,

00:09:20.341 --> 00:09:22.982
msukumo wa damu usoni hubadilika 
bila kujua.

00:09:23.613 --> 00:09:27.561
Na mabadiliko haya huendeshwa
kwa mfumo wa autonomiki

00:09:27.585 --> 00:09:29.754
ambayo ni nje ya uwezo wetu kudhibiti.

00:09:30.159 --> 00:09:33.982
Kwa kuangalia mabadiliko ya msukumo
wa damu usoni,

00:09:34.006 --> 00:09:36.703
tunaweza kuonyesha hisia za watu 
zilizojificha.

00:09:37.229 --> 00:09:42.007
Bahati mbaya, hisia hizo zinazohusiana
na mabadiliko ya msukumo wa damu usoni

00:09:42.031 --> 00:09:44.656
ni vigumu sana kugundua kwa macho yetu.

00:09:45.632 --> 00:09:49.400
Hivyo kusaidia kuonyesha
hisia za watu usoni,

00:09:49.424 --> 00:09:52.458
tumeunda teknolojia mpya ya picha

00:09:52.482 --> 00:09:55.631
tunaiita "tansderaml optical imaging"

00:09:56.679 --> 00:10:00.632
Kufanya hivyo tunatumia kamera ya video
ya kawaida kurekodi watu

00:10:00.656 --> 00:10:03.742
wanapokuwa na hisia mbalimbali
zilizojificha

00:10:04.385 --> 00:10:08.479
Na kisha, kwa kutumia teknolojia
ya usindikaji picha,

00:10:08.503 --> 00:10:14.039
tunaweza kupata picha kupitia ngozi
za mabadiliko ya msukumo wa damu usoni.

00:10:16.475 --> 00:10:20.747
Kwa kuangalia video za picha 
kupitia ngozi,

00:10:20.771 --> 00:10:22.558
sasa tunaweza kuona kwa urahisi

00:10:23.737 --> 00:10:29.368
mabadiliko ya msukumo wa damu usoni
yanayohusiana na hisia zilizojificha.

00:10:29.944 --> 00:10:31.732
Na kwa kutumia teknolojia hii,

00:10:31.756 --> 00:10:36.424
tunaweza kuonyesha hisia zilizojificha
zinazohusiana na udanganyifu,

00:10:36.448 --> 00:10:39.358
na kwahiyo kugundua uwongo wa watu.

00:10:39.382 --> 00:10:41.821
tunaweza kufanya bila upasuaji,

00:10:41.845 --> 00:10:44.384
kwa mbali, na gharama nafuu

00:10:44.408 --> 00:10:48.068
kwa usahihi wa takriban asilimia 85

00:10:48.092 --> 00:10:50.146
ambayo ni bora kuliko kubahatisha.

00:10:51.100 --> 00:10:54.890
Na kwa kuongezea, tumegundua
athari za Pinikio.

00:10:56.336 --> 00:10:58.391
Hapana, sio athari za Pinokio huyu.

00:10:58.415 --> 00:10:59.422
(Kicheko)

00:10:59.446 --> 00:11:01.568
Hizi ni athari za kweli za Pinokio.

00:11:01.592 --> 00:11:03.009
Wakati watu wanapodanganya,

00:11:03.033 --> 00:11:06.812
msukumo wa damu usoni
kwenye mashavu hupungua,

00:11:06.836 --> 00:11:10.097
na msukumo wa damu usoni
kwenye pua huongezeka.

00:11:11.379 --> 00:11:14.886
Hata hivyo, kudanganya sio tukio pekee

00:11:14.910 --> 00:11:17.758
ambalo litaamsha hisia zilizojificha.

00:11:17.782 --> 00:11:19.656
Hivyo basi tukajiuliza wenyewe,

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:22.027
pamoja na kugundua uwongo,

00:11:22.051 --> 00:11:24.384
teknolojia yetu inaweza kutumikaje?

00:11:25.027 --> 00:11:28.573
Utumikaji wake mmoja ni kwenye elimu.

00:11:28.597 --> 00:11:33.258
Kwa mfano, kwa kutumia teknolojia hii,
tunaweza kumsaidia mwalimu huyu wa hesabu

00:11:33.282 --> 00:11:36.189
kutambua wanafunzi darasani kwake

00:11:36.213 --> 00:11:40.958
wanapata woga mkubwa
kuhusu mada anayofundisha

00:11:40.982 --> 00:11:42.491
ili iweze kumsaidia.

00:11:43.337 --> 00:11:46.077
Na pia tunaweza kuitumia katika huduma
za afya.

00:11:46.101 --> 00:11:49.469
Mfano, kila siku natumia huduma ya
Skype kuwasilina na wazazi wangu,

00:11:49.493 --> 00:11:51.575
wanaoishi maelfu ya maili mbali.

00:11:52.178 --> 00:11:53.999
Na kwa kutumia teknolojia hii,

00:11:54.023 --> 00:11:57.505
Sio tu najua kinachoendelea
katika maisha yao

00:11:57.529 --> 00:12:03.831
lakini pia sambamba na kuangalia mapigo
yao ya moyo na kiwango cha msongo,

00:12:03.855 --> 00:12:07.080
hali zao na kama wanapata
au hawapati maumivu.

00:12:07.839 --> 00:12:09.649
Na pengine kwa siku za mbele,

00:12:09.673 --> 00:12:12.962
hatari za mshtuko wa moyo au
shinikizo la damu

00:12:13.701 --> 00:12:14.961
Na unaweza kuuliza:

00:12:15.472 --> 00:12:20.953
Tunaweza kutumia hii pia
kuonyesha hisia za wanasiasa?

00:12:20.977 --> 00:12:22.517
(Kicheko)

00:12:22.541 --> 00:12:24.395
Kwa mfano, wakati wa mijadala

00:12:25.220 --> 00:12:26.673
Kwakweli, jibu ni ndio.

00:12:27.167 --> 00:12:29.111
Kutumia kipande kinachorushwa
kwenye TV,

00:12:29.135 --> 00:12:33.181
tunaweza kugundua mapigo ya moyo
ya mwanasiasa,

00:12:33.205 --> 00:12:35.251
hali na msongo,

00:12:35.275 --> 00:12:38.853
na pengine katika siku za mbele.
iwe wanatudanganya au sivyo.

00:12:39.495 --> 00:12:42.491
Tunaweza pia kutumia hii
katika utafiti wa masoko,

00:12:42.515 --> 00:12:44.366
kwa mfano, kujua

00:12:44.390 --> 00:12:48.745
kama watu wanapenda au hawapendi
bidhaa fulani za matumizi.

00:12:49.229 --> 00:12:51.467
Tunaweza hata kutumia kwenye miadi.

00:12:51.904 --> 00:12:53.064
Sasa kwa mfano

00:12:53.088 --> 00:12:55.682
Ikiwa mliyeahidiana anakuonyesha tabasamu,

00:12:55.706 --> 00:12:58.500
teknolojia hii inaweza kukusaidia kujua

00:12:58.524 --> 00:13:01.131
kama anakupenda kweli

00:13:01.155 --> 00:13:03.330
au anajaribu tu kuonyesha wema kwako.

00:13:03.864 --> 00:13:05.559
Na kwa suala hili,

00:13:05.583 --> 00:13:07.459
anajaribu kuonyesha wema kwako.

00:13:07.483 --> 00:13:09.875
(Kicheko)

00:13:11.244 --> 00:13:14.953
Hivyo teknolojia ya transdermal optical
imaging

00:13:14.977 --> 00:13:17.555
iko katika hatua za mwanzo za kuendelezwa.

00:13:17.579 --> 00:13:21.693
Matumizi mengi mapya yatakuja
ambayo hatuyajui leo.

00:13:22.293 --> 00:13:25.071
Ingawa, kitu kimoja ninachojua kwa uhakika

00:13:25.095 --> 00:13:28.509
ni kwamba kudanganya
hakutakuwa kama zamani tena.

00:13:28.533 --> 00:13:29.685
Asanteni sana.

00:13:29.715 --> 00:13:30.949
Asanteni.

00:13:31.059 --> 00:13:34.969
(Makofi)

